{"tid":1673884,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［行動po建議］11月12曰 國父 孫中山 誕辰記念 集會","createTime":"2019-10-25T01:53:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T01:53:59.000Z","uid":104440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bc80bb864bff5040fe65d72dc36f738a85ee3e19","tid":1673884,"uid":104440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T01:53:59.000Z","msg":"建議 11月12曰 都搞返個集會活動<br />\n<br />\n國父 孫中山 先生 誕辰記念日 <br />\n竟然無人記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n97之前 仲要係公眾假期 有假放<br />\n依家比大陸食左 仲取消埋 <br />\n搞到依家無人知 無人記得<br />\n<br />\n一個中國 得一個國父<br />\n仲要係中國民主革命領袖<br />\n竟然無人提<br />\n<br />\n雖然唔係星期六日<br />\n但都想有個活動集會<br />\n等大家唔好忘記<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n革命尚未成功 同志仍須努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}